16:31.719 --> 16:35.264
Jesus told them, this is the only work God wants from you.

16:36.025 --> 16:38.709
Believe in the one he has sent.

16:39.970 --> 16:43.735
They answered, well, show us a miraculous sign if you want us to believe in you.

16:44.496 --> 16:45.137
What can you do?

16:45.197 --> 16:49.563
After all, our ancestors ate manna while they journeyed through the wilderness.

16:50.264 --> 16:52.988
The scriptures say Moses gave them bread from heaven to eat.

16:53.649 --> 16:54.610
You hear what they're doing.

16:55.330 --> 16:58.053
